snippet.title: Dstroy - (1997) - World_06
snippet.description:
Short video of levels #26 to #30 from Dstroy (1997) on Ms-Dos, This time the boss of the 6th world is waiting for you at the end of the video.
---------------------------------------------
Play Dstroy on your browser: https://archive.org/details/msdos_Dstroy_1995
Music by Jerome Angelot: https://soundcloud.com/jerome-angelot
You can find all Dstroy's music here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLRPnyG742soucre6fCetGiB0BvYO87HvR
